Title: Cold Blooded
Plot: The CSI team investigate the murder of a man whose daughter was killed five years ago, and the bizarre death of a young man who appears to have been killed by a T-Rex.
ParentalRatingReason: R16 Violence and content that may disturb
GuestStars: Jessica Hecht, Nora Kirkpatrick, James Immekus, Nate Hartley, Brett Tucker, Marta Martin, William R. Moses, Jon Wellner, Katee Sackhoff
